{"tid":1256804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"某個大國口交部常用經典回應實錄","createTime":"2019-06-25T08:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T11:04:14.000Z","uid":264426,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31ae43a6c0638b61bd74d6bf19925311a72711b9","tid":1256804,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"台灣交往法案&rdquo;嚴重違反一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中方對此強烈不滿和堅決反對，已向美方提出嚴正交涉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中方<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敦促</span></span>美方恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報的規定，慎重妥善處理涉台問題。<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸以來，&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;、&ldquo;港人治港&rdquo;、高度自治方針得到切實貫徹落實，香港居民享有的各項權利和自由依法得到充分保障，事實有目共睹。保持香港繁榮穩定，不僅符合中國的利益，也符合世界各國的利益。同時，我想強調，香港是中國的特別行政區，香港事務純屬<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國內政，任何國家、組織和個人都無權干預。</span></span>中方維護國家主權、安全和發展利益、維護香港繁榮穩定的決心堅定不移<br />\n<br />\n#中國內政<br />\n#強烈不滿<br />\n#堅決反對<br />\n#一個中國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6129b3323cb5623ba8ad90ae0f739e6b81bb96","tid":1256804,"uid":264426,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"佢地今年仲好鐘意用干預呢兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2cff45f5fe4b5b2d9002e2a4824e1d3fd3caa9","tid":1256804,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"嚴正交涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b04de0c49a7611d86ab73d0b67a4555cda0ae","tid":1256804,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"巨嬰發爛渣 <img src=\